verbose_text: The baseline uptake of non metabolizable hexose was 0.33 +/- 0.07 nmol 2-DG/100 mg lipids/10 min, it was increased up to 0.70 +/- 0.20 by methylamine 1 mM, and reached 3.24 +/- 0.63 nmol 2-DG/100 mg lipids/10 min with 100 nM insulin (n = 4, p < 0.01).
